{"title":"Bolt of Fire","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Bolt_of_Fire","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.30](/0.30 \"0.30\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n|   |                                     |\n| - | ----------------------------------- |\n|   | Fires a penetrating bolt of flames. |\n\n**Bolt of Fire** is a monster-only spell capable of striking multiple targets along its path, dealing a considerable amount of [fire](/Fire \"Fire\") damage. [Fire resistance](/Fire#Fire_Resistance \"Fire\") reduces the damage dealt by this spell by 50% (rF+), 66% (rF++), or 80% (rF+++). The [Fire Breath](/Fire_Breath \"Fire Breath\") monster ability is very similar to this spell.\n\nLike other types of Fire Magic, bolts of fire that pass through [water](/Water \"Water\") will create [steam](/Steam \"Steam\"), and are negated by [freezing clouds](/Freezing_vapour \"Freezing vapour\").\n\nThe following enemies cast Bolt of Fire:\n\n- & [![Asmodeus.png](/images/3/34/Asmodeus.png)](/File:Asmodeus.png) **[Asmodeus](/Asmodeus \"Asmodeus\")** (3d26 damage)\n- R [![Azrael.png](/images/f/fa/Azrael.png)](/File:Azrael.png) **[Azrael](/Azrael \"Azrael\")** (3d20 damage)\n- 2 [![Balrug.png](/images/2/21/Balrug.png)](/File:Balrug.png) **[Balrug](/Balrug \"Balrug\")** (3d23 damage)\n- e [![Deep elf pyromancer.png](/images/a/aa/Deep_elf_pyromancer.png)](/File:Deep_elf_pyromancer.png) **[Deep elf pyromancer](/Deep_elf_pyromancer \"Deep elf pyromancer\")** (3d17 damage)\n- q [![Draconian scorcher.png](/images/1/11/Draconian_scorcher.png)](/File:Draconian_scorcher.png) **[Draconian scorcher](/Draconian_scorcher \"Draconian scorcher\")** (3d25 damage)\n- R [![Efreet.png](/images/f/f9/Efreet.png)](/File:Efreet.png) **[Efreet](/Efreet \"Efreet\")** (3d15 damage)\n- C [![Fire giant.png](/images/1/16/Fire_giant.png)](/File:Fire_giant.png) **[Fire giant](/Fire_giant \"Fire giant\")** (3d25 damage)\n- D [![Golden dragon.png